sentences: Prior to moving to Athens, Dottie graduated from Westover Senior High School in Fayetteville, North Carolina in 1990.
On July 26, 2009, long-time boyfriend and of Montreal video editor and stage performer Nick Gould proposed during an of Montreal show at the Hollywood Bowl.
The wedding took place in May 2010.
Both Dottie and James joined of Montreal in 1998.
In 1997, Dottie contributed to Kindercore's first Christmas in Stereo album under the My First Keyboard moniker.
